This paper is about information retrieval using language models, which is a core topic in the field of information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also discusses the use of clustering to improve the language models, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.CL) and data mining (cs.DS). The paper also proposes new algorithms that improve the performance of the language models, which is a topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG).
